title: Full Tank Warwick Does Carry Damage
body: Kind of ridiculous when you can have 6 tank items and your ult plus 2 autos can 100-0 a squishy, and you can easily kill any fighter if you build a thornmail. Not sure what riot was thinking. You'd think they'd have already sold enough WW skins to not worry about making him OP for a bit.

replies.body: WARWICK WAS BUULDING FULL TANK. I KNOW THIS BECAUSE I WAS PLAYING EZREAL AND HE WASNT TAKING ANY DAMAGE FROM ME BECAUSE ALL OF MY ABILITIES MISSED.
Well he did build a {{item:3748}} after building tank.
Is it that a full tank warwick does carry damage, or that a squishy has so little defense they take full carry damage?
What items do you have and what items does the WW have exactly? Also, what champ are you?
